The '''Montenegrin Embassy inTirana''' ([[Montenegrin language|Montenegrin]]: Ambasada Crne Gore u Tirani) is [[Montenegro]]'s diplomatic mission to the [[Albania]]. It is located at Rr. Jul Varibova 11.

The current Ambassador of Montenegro to the Albania is [[Željko Perović]].

